"'''Lurking in the Shadows: The Creatures of Episode III'''" was an article written by [[Daniel Wallace]] and was featured in [[Star Wars Insider 84]]. It provided in-universe as well as behind the scenes information to some of the various creatures that were featured in [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']].

